        heading: "The Temp-to-Perm Opportunity",
        content: "Temporary work isn't just a job—it's often an audition for permanent employment.\n\n### Conversion Statistics\n\n| Metric | Data |\n|--------|------|\n| Temp workers converting to permanent | 40% nationally |\n| Companies preferring to hire former temps | 67% |\n| Temp-to-perm happening within 6 months | 52% |\n| Employers with formal temp-to-perm programs | 45% |\n\n### Why Companies Love Hiring Temps Permanently\n\n1. **Try before you buy** – They've seen you in action\n2. **Cultural fit proven** – You already work with the team\n3. **Training complete** – No ramp-up time needed\n4. **Reduced risk** – They know your reliability\n5. **Faster hiring** – No lengthy recruitment process\n\n### Indeed Flex to Permanent Pathway\n\nOn [Indeed Flex](https://indeedflex.com/download-app/), permanent opportunities emerge through:\n\n- **Talent Pools** – Companies add top performers for repeat work\n- **Direct offers** – Managers can reach out about permanent roles\n- **Relationship building** – Multiple shifts = relationship development\n\n> **Key Insight:** Your Indeed Flex rating is visible proof of your work quality. A 4.9+ rating with 50+ shifts is a compelling case for permanent employment."
